											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player stops, confused, as Minthara comes lurching towards them from the darkness of the undercity. She is bloodied, bruised, clutching a wound on her side - something terrible has happened to her. In the distance, we hear a strange giggle (Orin)." />
